WEBVTT

01:25.690 --> 01:35.000
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.360 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 21]

01:39.539 --> 01:39.979
Hello.

01:40.650 --> 01:41.200
Hello.

01:41.280 --> 01:41.680
Hello.

01:41.850 --> 01:42.539
I've also been

01:42.539 --> 01:44.979
selling goods in the market lately.

01:45.539 --> 01:46.289
I'm a vendor like you

01:46.289 --> 01:47.570
and a fellow countryman.

01:47.570 --> 01:48.210
We're all Chinese.

01:48.210 --> 01:49.039
Nice to meet you.

01:49.039 --> 01:49.840
My surname is Du.

01:49.840 --> 01:51.100
You can just call me Du.

01:52.210 --> 01:53.210
How may I help you?

01:54.920 --> 01:56.580
I meant to say hello to you guys

01:57.140 --> 01:58.600
on the day of your arrival.

01:58.950 --> 02:01.100
But your stall was too popular.

02:01.340 --> 02:03.180
I didn't even manage to squeeze in.

02:03.180 --> 02:04.640
How kind of you to say that.

02:04.840 --> 02:05.780
It's pretty cold out here.

02:05.780 --> 02:06.730
Would you like to talk inside?

02:06.730 --> 02:08.330
No, no. I'm not going inside.

02:08.630 --> 02:09.300
See,

02:09.680 --> 02:11.610
you guys have been here for a while.

02:11.690 --> 02:12.410
Well,

02:12.680 --> 02:14.000
there's a nice Chinese restaurant

02:14.000 --> 02:14.630
nearby.

02:15.240 --> 02:16.840
How about we have a gathering there?

02:16.840 --> 02:18.060
We are all Chinese, aren't we?

02:18.060 --> 02:19.460
We can eat and talk there.

02:19.520 --> 02:19.960
Hello.

02:20.190 --> 02:20.650
Sir.

02:20.860 --> 02:21.790
What's going on?

02:22.280 --> 02:24.740
This is Mr. Du,
a fellow vendor in the market.

02:25.090 --> 02:25.970
Just call me Du.

02:26.360 --> 02:27.890
He's inviting us to dinner.

02:28.800 --> 02:30.280
There is no time like the present.

02:30.280 --> 02:31.140
Shall we go now?

02:33.460 --> 02:34.210
Mr. Du.

02:35.190 --> 02:35.500
Jun.

02:35.500 --> 02:36.630
Why talk by the door?

02:36.930 --> 02:37.810
You know each other?

02:37.810 --> 02:38.400
Yes.

02:39.860 --> 02:40.310
Mr. Du

02:40.360 --> 02:41.579
is quite famous in our circle

02:41.579 --> 02:42.740
of resellers.

02:43.770 --> 02:45.340
Jun's here too, huh?

02:45.340 --> 02:45.860
Everyone is here.

02:45.860 --> 02:46.530
Let's go eat.

02:46.530 --> 02:47.240
Let's go then.

02:47.240 --> 02:47.960
We can eat and talk

02:47.960 --> 02:49.370
in that Chinese restaurant.

02:49.370 --> 02:50.500
Are you that hungry?

02:50.650 --> 02:51.800
Isn't he a fellow countryman?

02:51.800 --> 02:53.150
Seriously, dining with a random guy?

02:53.150 --> 02:53.900
If you're going out to eat,

02:53.900 --> 02:55.700
shouldn't you run it by me first?

02:56.410 --> 02:56.970
Mr. Du.

02:58.130 --> 02:59.340
Just cut to the chase.

03:00.840 --> 03:02.000
Time is money.

03:03.020 --> 03:04.810
Right. I do have something

03:04.810 --> 03:05.940
to discuss with you.

03:06.430 --> 03:08.710
I sell leather shoes,

03:09.080 --> 03:10.810
and I'd like to team up with you.

03:13.910 --> 03:16.030
Come on, look at my shoes.

03:16.810 --> 03:18.940
See if they can be added to your outfits

03:19.130 --> 03:20.800
and sell more with your help, okay?

03:20.800 --> 03:21.400
This is...

03:21.560 --> 03:22.820
mutually beneficial.

03:23.930 --> 03:24.590
Take a look.

03:27.470 --> 03:28.530
The shoes are nice.

03:33.530 --> 03:34.370
Sorry,

03:34.560 --> 03:36.030
we don't sell leather shoes.

03:36.030 --> 03:36.890
Take them back.

03:42.000 --> 03:42.930
What do you mean?

03:43.860 --> 03:44.920
We're all Chinese.

03:45.280 --> 03:46.880
Why not make money together?

03:47.579 --> 03:50.110
It's not a decent move
to keep all the benefits

03:50.690 --> 03:51.579
to yourselves.

03:53.020 --> 03:53.710
Du,

03:54.280 --> 03:55.630
it's rude of you to say that.

03:55.630 --> 03:56.500
How am I rude?

03:57.030 --> 03:57.740
We sell outfits,

03:57.740 --> 03:58.800
not leather shoes.

03:59.030 --> 04:00.190
We're not standing in your way.

04:00.190 --> 04:00.680
No,

04:00.810 --> 04:02.810
-my only purpose here is...
-Mr. Du.

04:03.840 --> 04:05.060
These leather shoes of yours

04:05.060 --> 04:07.150
are called flashy junk
in where we're from.

04:07.150 --> 04:08.800
They can only last for a short time.

04:08.800 --> 04:09.970
We refuse to sell anything

04:09.970 --> 04:10.830
of low quality.

04:13.710 --> 04:14.240
Indeed.

04:15.410 --> 04:17.010
But quality doesn't matter,

04:17.220 --> 04:18.720
as long as the goods can sell.

04:18.720 --> 04:19.329
Right?

04:20.070 --> 04:21.800
It's not like we're tricking Chinese.

04:21.800 --> 04:23.650
Why are you being so serious?

04:23.680 --> 04:25.000
Let's just make money.

04:25.430 --> 04:27.040
You are truly a disgrace to us Chinese.

04:27.040 --> 04:27.430
I...

04:27.870 --> 04:29.310
Very well said.

04:30.120 --> 04:31.380
Alright. Liangliang,

04:31.560 --> 04:32.560
see the guest out.

04:33.130 --> 04:33.620
Mr. Du.

04:33.680 --> 04:34.159
No...

04:34.950 --> 04:38.060
See you later.

04:38.330 --> 04:38.990
No, wait...

04:41.130 --> 04:42.659
What kind of person is that?

04:42.810 --> 04:44.690
He looks self-righteous
though he sells fakes.

04:44.690 --> 04:45.420
Don't be mad.

04:45.830 --> 04:46.860
His goods are of poor quality.

04:46.860 --> 04:48.430
There won't be return customers.

04:48.430 --> 04:49.250
Over time,

04:49.330 --> 04:50.220
the reputation of Chinese merchants

04:50.220 --> 04:51.870
in overseas markets will be damaged.

04:51.870 --> 04:52.560
There is so much

04:52.560 --> 04:53.690
good stuff in China.

04:53.800 --> 04:54.810
Why does he have to sell fakes?

04:54.810 --> 04:55.420
Listen,

04:55.510 --> 04:56.390
these days,

04:56.420 --> 04:57.720
Chinese merchandise is selling better

04:57.720 --> 04:58.430
and better in Russia.

04:58.430 --> 04:59.950
The market is getting bigger and bigger.

04:59.950 --> 05:00.610
Meanwhile,

05:00.630 --> 05:02.100
all kinds of shady people are showing up.

05:02.100 --> 05:03.450
There are many, many unscrupulous traders.

05:03.450 --> 05:03.980
Previously,

05:03.980 --> 05:05.310
a batch of down jackets came from China.

05:05.310 --> 05:07.250
Yet there aren't many feathers in them.

05:07.250 --> 05:08.190
See, Russians have to endure

05:08.190 --> 05:08.860
cold winters here.

05:08.860 --> 05:09.890
Some kids wore those clothes and said,

05:09.890 --> 05:10.510
"I hate the clothes

05:10.510 --> 05:11.540
sold by Chinese people the most."

05:11.540 --> 05:12.890
That's awful to hear, isn't it?

05:12.890 --> 05:13.770
How embarrassing.

05:13.770 --> 05:14.430
Yes.

05:15.220 --> 05:17.860
When the reputation is gone,
everything is gone.

05:17.860 --> 05:19.000
This must be Sophia, right?

05:19.000 --> 05:19.660
Zhuang Zhuang,

05:19.660 --> 05:20.740
let me get the door.

05:22.040 --> 05:23.440
Shall we heat up the food?

05:28.310 --> 05:29.180
What are you doing?

05:29.180 --> 05:30.510
What do you mean by this?

05:33.600 --> 05:34.310
Who are you?

05:34.370 --> 05:35.890
Don't move! Back off!

05:36.540 --> 05:38.190
Stop there!

05:40.100 --> 05:40.740
Let go!

05:41.500 --> 05:42.120
Let go!

05:42.190 --> 05:43.330
Let go of him right now!

05:43.330 --> 05:44.060
Let go of him!

05:44.860 --> 05:45.630
Shut up.

05:49.390 --> 05:49.920
Let go.

05:51.600 --> 05:52.730
Liangliang, let go.

05:53.130 --> 05:54.100
Liangliang, let go.

05:54.100 --> 05:55.370
Hands off.

05:59.740 --> 06:02.630
Seems like many people are after you.

06:03.720 --> 06:05.390
Sophia lent this place to you,

06:05.560 --> 06:06.370
didn't she?

06:06.570 --> 06:07.300
Where is she?

06:08.240 --> 06:09.810
I meant to talk to her.

06:12.740 --> 06:13.620
Mr. Sergey,

06:14.370 --> 06:15.300
long time no see.

06:17.890 --> 06:18.540
What?

06:19.040 --> 06:20.300
You're still in this area?

06:20.300 --> 06:21.400
This is my turf.

06:21.560 --> 06:23.570
Where else would I be?

06:23.800 --> 06:25.390
As you Chinese always say,

06:26.100 --> 06:28.230
everyone should get a piece of the pie.

06:29.480 --> 06:32.010
But you keep making money yourself
in secret.

06:34.130 --> 06:35.530
That's not appropriate.

06:35.659 --> 06:36.430
I heard

06:36.980 --> 06:37.750
your goods

06:38.070 --> 06:39.800
have been selling well lately.

06:40.100 --> 06:42.659
You've made a name for yourself
in our market.

06:44.040 --> 06:45.970
With all that money you've earned,

06:47.500 --> 06:49.360
a small token of appreciation...

06:49.870 --> 06:50.670
is called for.

06:51.570 --> 06:53.230
Isn't it only fitting to do so?

06:56.620 --> 06:57.680
Yes, you're right.

06:58.810 --> 07:00.600
But don't you usually collect fees

07:00.600 --> 07:02.010
directly from the stall?

07:02.860 --> 07:03.860
We really didn't see you when we were

07:03.860 --> 07:05.360
doing business here this time.

07:05.360 --> 07:07.890
We thought you were off
making a fortune elsewhere.

07:07.890 --> 07:09.690
We're both trying to earn money.

07:09.920 --> 07:11.920
you didn't have to bring a gang here.

07:12.120 --> 07:12.630
Look,

07:13.500 --> 07:14.390
why not just tell us

07:14.390 --> 07:15.990
what we can do to satisfy you?

07:17.600 --> 07:18.040
Right.

07:18.430 --> 07:19.510
It's our first time

07:19.510 --> 07:20.710
doing business here.

07:21.160 --> 07:21.810
We don't know

07:21.810 --> 07:23.180
much about your rules.

07:24.800 --> 07:25.600
Pretty smart.

07:29.370 --> 07:32.010
But it's a bit too late, isn't it?

07:33.120 --> 07:34.070
Now, you guys

07:35.240 --> 07:37.170
have really livened up the market.

07:37.330 --> 07:38.530
Everyone has seen it.

07:38.830 --> 07:40.430
You've earned a good amount,

07:40.620 --> 07:42.350
yet you've never paid me a dime.

07:42.890 --> 07:45.210
How am I supposed
to manage the market then?

07:45.210 --> 07:46.140
Should I just...

07:46.630 --> 07:48.180
let everyone make money here

07:48.180 --> 07:49.310
and leave without a price?

07:49.310 --> 07:50.540
What are you trying to say?

07:50.540 --> 07:51.920
-Get to point.
-Quiet.

07:53.950 --> 07:57.280
Yes, we've made some money.

07:59.870 --> 08:00.600
I know.

08:01.070 --> 08:02.000
I know the rules.

08:02.810 --> 08:04.180
How about this?

08:05.220 --> 08:06.550
Harmony brings wealth.

08:07.300 --> 08:08.300
Just name a price.

08:08.690 --> 08:09.250
Okay.

08:10.920 --> 08:13.300
"Harmony brings wealth." That sounds good.

08:13.300 --> 08:15.560
I'd like to sell what you're selling now.

08:16.570 --> 08:17.930
I also want to make big money.

08:17.930 --> 08:19.630
That makes our conversation easier.

08:19.630 --> 08:21.160
Bring your goods over then.

08:21.190 --> 08:22.220
We'll sell them for you.

08:22.220 --> 08:23.330
We'll do all the hard work

08:23.330 --> 08:23.890
free of charge.

08:23.890 --> 08:25.390
All the profits will be yours.

08:25.390 --> 08:26.650
Or you can just join us.

08:26.680 --> 08:27.720
Put in an investment,

08:27.720 --> 08:29.240
and we'll split the earnings with you.

08:29.240 --> 08:29.970
Is that okay?

08:32.250 --> 08:33.850
What if I don't invest at all?

08:36.460 --> 08:37.120
Mr. Sergey,

08:37.940 --> 08:39.940
we have to pay a lot for our supplies.

08:40.100 --> 08:41.150
If you are to partner with us,

08:41.150 --> 08:42.480
you have to invest a sum.

08:42.700 --> 08:44.230
Or it won't be fair, will it?

08:46.500 --> 08:48.030
Who said I wouldn't invest?

08:48.650 --> 08:50.290
The money you've made here

08:51.030 --> 08:52.150
is my capital.

08:53.150 --> 08:55.210
Your business is soaring these days.

08:55.600 --> 08:56.250
You must've

08:56.250 --> 08:57.780
accumulated much capital.

08:57.910 --> 09:00.030
Plus, I have many sales channels

09:00.480 --> 09:02.280
that can help you make big money.

09:02.770 --> 09:04.170
When there's an earning,

09:05.390 --> 09:06.720
I'll probably consider

09:07.080 --> 09:08.680
sharing the profits with you

09:09.010 --> 09:11.580
or returning the capital to you.

09:16.770 --> 09:17.430
Mr. Sergey,

09:18.630 --> 09:19.830
to tell you the truth,

09:21.700 --> 09:23.030
our goods have sold out.

09:25.390 --> 09:26.160
Now, if we are

09:26.480 --> 09:27.840
to get a new batch,

09:28.630 --> 09:30.630
it'll likely take more than 10 days.

09:32.390 --> 09:33.070
Well,

09:34.030 --> 09:36.160
there is still some time until winter.

09:36.340 --> 09:38.740
I'll give you...15 days.

09:39.600 --> 09:40.100
Okay.

09:41.250 --> 09:42.450
Then you must promise

09:43.250 --> 09:43.870
not to cause us

09:43.870 --> 09:45.600
any trouble in the next 15 days.

09:46.120 --> 09:47.740
I'll make sure you receive a huge return.

09:47.740 --> 09:48.410
After all,

09:49.530 --> 09:50.460
before we came to do business here,

09:50.460 --> 09:51.790
we hadn't informed you.

09:51.890 --> 09:52.950
That was our fault.

09:54.150 --> 09:54.890
Ma Xiaojun.

09:56.530 --> 09:58.790
You really are smart.

09:59.940 --> 10:01.750
But I have to say this again:

10:03.250 --> 10:04.740
don't get clever with me.

10:19.010 --> 10:19.600
Hold it.

10:28.240 --> 10:29.040
They're gone.

10:31.440 --> 10:32.750
If we weren't in Russia

10:33.860 --> 10:35.080
but Beijing,

10:36.030 --> 10:37.630
I would've slapped that guy,

10:37.870 --> 10:39.580
regardless of who he is.

10:40.240 --> 10:40.940
Xiaojun,

10:41.740 --> 10:42.550
previously,

10:42.550 --> 10:44.390
Sergey's turf expanded again.

10:45.090 --> 10:46.120
He's been collecting

10:46.120 --> 10:48.700
protection fees arbitrarily
in the nearby markets.

10:48.700 --> 10:51.240
He particularly hates
to see foreigners make money.

10:51.240 --> 10:52.510
To add to that, you've been faring so well

10:52.510 --> 10:53.670
in your business lately.

10:53.670 --> 10:56.130
I'm sure he won't easily
let you off the hook.

10:57.150 --> 10:58.560
If we partner with him,

10:58.870 --> 10:59.580
he definitely won't

10:59.580 --> 11:00.510
share profits with us.

11:00.510 --> 11:02.170
He's practically robbing us.

11:02.720 --> 11:05.080
Can't someone do something
about these people?

11:05.080 --> 11:05.940
How about this?

11:06.510 --> 11:07.240
Let's not...

11:07.390 --> 11:09.140
cause trouble for Sophia

11:09.370 --> 11:10.980
or ourselves.

11:11.010 --> 11:12.340
Since you've made Sergey a promise,

11:12.340 --> 11:13.510
we might as well give him money

11:13.510 --> 11:15.110
and retreat back to Beijing.

11:16.000 --> 11:18.570
Composure is a must in doing business.

11:18.790 --> 11:19.990
What's this rush for?

11:20.770 --> 11:21.650
I admit that at first,

11:21.650 --> 11:23.250
I was quite afraid of Sergey.

11:23.740 --> 11:24.700
I feared nothing

11:25.000 --> 11:25.720
but that he might

11:25.720 --> 11:26.630
take away all the money

11:26.630 --> 11:27.760
you worked hard for.

11:28.220 --> 11:29.080
Think about it.

11:29.890 --> 11:30.650
He has no idea of the amount

11:30.650 --> 11:31.670
of the capital in our hands.

11:31.670 --> 11:32.370
Neither is he aware

11:32.370 --> 11:33.370
of where we get our suppliers

11:33.370 --> 11:34.530
or how many goods we'll buy.

11:34.530 --> 11:36.130
He doesn't need to know that.

11:36.130 --> 11:37.580
He already considers your money and goods

11:37.580 --> 11:39.620
to be his
whether you continue the business or not.

11:39.620 --> 11:41.080
Plus, you've already made him a promise.

11:41.080 --> 11:42.770
What's the point of talking tough here?

11:42.770 --> 11:43.240
Come on.

11:43.250 --> 11:45.110
Don't chime in when I'm speaking.

11:45.150 --> 11:46.080
Come here, come.

11:46.120 --> 11:46.850
Take my seat.

11:47.980 --> 11:48.580
Be seated.

11:53.360 --> 11:55.220
Here's my thought on this matter.

11:55.410 --> 11:56.770
We should continue to pick up goods

11:56.770 --> 11:57.770
from Vladivostok

11:58.010 --> 11:59.670
and keep on with our business.

12:00.150 --> 12:01.360
No risk, no reward.

12:01.720 --> 12:02.360
Jun,

12:03.030 --> 12:03.720
I remember

12:03.720 --> 12:06.580
you saying that shipment
from Vladivostok is huge.

12:08.240 --> 12:09.630
Are you planning to save a batch

12:09.630 --> 12:10.840
for us to sell on our own?

12:10.840 --> 12:11.370
Exactly!

12:12.820 --> 12:13.870
You all know how beautiful

12:13.870 --> 12:14.550
and kind Sophia is.

12:14.550 --> 12:15.290
But what you don't know

12:15.290 --> 12:16.130
is that she is actually

12:16.130 --> 12:17.390
a great businesswoman

12:17.670 --> 12:19.480
with a good reputation and credibility.

12:19.480 --> 12:21.610
Sophia, I'd like to ask you for a favor.

12:22.100 --> 12:23.360
Could you introduce us

12:23.720 --> 12:25.000
to the merchants you know who are nice

12:25.000 --> 12:26.130
and capable of handling a massive deal

12:26.130 --> 12:26.960
like this, so we can

12:26.960 --> 12:28.220
talk to them ourselves?

12:28.220 --> 12:29.820
The more familiar they're with you,
the better.

12:29.820 --> 12:31.840
They have to be so close to you
that Sergey doesn't even

12:31.840 --> 12:32.790
know of or has met them,

12:32.790 --> 12:35.450
to the extent where they'd agree
to talk at home.

12:36.550 --> 12:38.390
Your goods are of high quality,

12:39.030 --> 12:40.830
and you've risen to fame lately.

12:41.740 --> 12:43.940
It shouldn't be hard to do what you said.

12:43.960 --> 12:44.530
Look,

12:44.910 --> 12:46.970
Sophia has done us a huge favor again.

12:47.120 --> 12:47.940
How about this?

12:47.940 --> 12:49.400
When we go back to Beijing,

12:50.150 --> 12:51.480
we'll leave Jun with you

12:51.480 --> 12:53.620
as a gift from us. Okay?

12:54.500 --> 12:55.480
You... I...

12:55.620 --> 12:57.000
See, you two are really...

12:57.000 --> 12:58.600
No, we're just good friends.

12:58.630 --> 13:01.130
-It's only right to help each other.
-Yes, we’re good friends.

13:01.130 --> 13:02.590
You seem quite happy to me.

13:03.360 --> 13:04.020
However...

13:05.940 --> 13:07.940
be clear about the ugly truth first.

13:08.100 --> 13:09.560
There are bound to be risks

13:10.250 --> 13:12.170
in doing business.

13:13.130 --> 13:14.220
If in the end,

13:14.240 --> 13:15.770
we lose everything, you...

13:16.620 --> 13:17.650
Jun, stop it.

13:17.980 --> 13:19.370
We'll take it as a life experience then.

13:19.370 --> 13:20.000
Yes.

13:20.250 --> 13:20.980
Bumps are inevitable

13:20.980 --> 13:22.500
along the road of business.

13:22.500 --> 13:25.160
We're good friends,
and we're in this together.

13:25.220 --> 13:26.080
Let's go for it!

13:28.200 --> 13:29.730
What you said has really...

13:30.410 --> 13:31.720
warmed my heart.

13:33.240 --> 13:34.370
Let's go for it then!

13:34.650 --> 13:35.710
Here is my idea.

13:35.890 --> 13:37.250
Tomorrow, you'll go to Vladivostok

13:37.250 --> 13:38.320
to pick up that large shipment.

13:38.320 --> 13:39.500
Then, have it

13:39.670 --> 13:40.490
covertly

13:40.630 --> 13:41.840
delivered here in batches.

13:41.840 --> 13:42.890
You can go back to Beijing afterwards

13:42.890 --> 13:43.870
and wait to hear from us.

13:43.870 --> 13:44.620
As for us, we...

13:44.620 --> 13:45.250
No, wait, Jun.

13:45.250 --> 13:46.220
How can you assign

13:46.220 --> 13:47.010
such a big task to me?

13:47.010 --> 13:48.200
You think I'm silly or what?

13:48.200 --> 13:49.460
Sergey is a terrible menace.

13:49.460 --> 13:50.720
Won't it make me a deserter

13:50.720 --> 13:52.030
before battle if I leave?

13:52.030 --> 13:52.910
I must stay here

13:52.940 --> 13:53.780
by your side.

13:53.890 --> 13:55.270
Didn't you say you'd listen to me?

13:55.270 --> 13:56.700
Can I pick up the goods myself?

13:56.700 --> 13:58.150
I have to stay here for negotiations,
don't I?

13:58.150 --> 13:58.790
Besides,

13:58.840 --> 14:01.170
I must protect Sophia.

14:01.220 --> 14:03.510
Can we have Zhuang Zhuang
take on the task?

14:03.510 --> 14:04.720
Shengli will definitely disagree, right?

14:04.720 --> 14:05.250
If we let Shengli do it,

14:05.250 --> 14:06.050
Zhuang Zhuang won't agree with it.

14:06.050 --> 14:06.890
Should we let them both go back?

14:06.890 --> 14:08.010
Yes, that's right.

14:08.010 --> 14:08.980
I'll stick with you.

14:08.980 --> 14:09.710
How about...

14:09.770 --> 14:10.920
we hold a vote then?

14:11.100 --> 14:12.620
Raise your hand if you agree
that Zhuang Zhuang and Shengli

14:12.620 --> 14:13.750
should go together.

14:14.170 --> 14:16.230
Raise your hand
if you think Liangliang should go.

14:16.230 --> 14:17.150
Alright, it's settled.

14:17.150 --> 14:18.360
It's time I talked about the next steps.

14:18.360 --> 14:18.670
Sit.

14:21.030 --> 14:22.120
Coming!

14:25.410 --> 14:27.450
Long time no see.

14:27.940 --> 14:30.010
Hello, long time no see.

14:30.050 --> 14:31.850
Today has been a really long day.

14:44.370 --> 14:45.410
Okay. Thank you.

15:02.170 --> 15:03.030
Please come in.

15:04.270 --> 15:04.940
Hello!

15:05.500 --> 15:06.050
Hello.

15:06.240 --> 15:07.770
Take a seat. Nice to meet you.

15:07.770 --> 15:09.000
I'm Ma Xiaojun, also known as Lucky Ma.

15:09.000 --> 15:09.820
That is Ma Xiaojun.

15:09.820 --> 15:10.320
Hello.

15:10.790 --> 15:11.320
Hello.

15:13.790 --> 15:15.410
These two leather jackets

15:15.410 --> 15:16.880
are our best sellers recently.

15:16.880 --> 15:18.080
Top sellers, indeed.

15:31.400 --> 15:33.870
[No standing under suspended loads]

15:42.290 --> 15:43.360
Admiring your looks again, huh?

15:43.360 --> 15:44.120
What did you buy?

15:44.120 --> 15:44.890
Check it out.

15:46.670 --> 15:47.750
What are we having for dinner?

15:47.750 --> 15:48.460
Borscht?

15:48.670 --> 15:49.840
Sure. Sounds great!

15:49.950 --> 15:51.030
I'll go find a restaurant for you then.

15:51.030 --> 15:51.410
Okay.

17:23.089 --> 17:24.310
If you don't have better things to do,

17:24.310 --> 17:25.810
go out for a smoke.

17:27.700 --> 17:29.310
Boss, I've got some news.

17:29.310 --> 17:30.960
We found the money.

17:30.960 --> 17:32.350
They hid it somewhere.

17:33.000 --> 17:33.900
These people enjoy nothing

17:33.900 --> 17:35.230
but being smarty pants.

17:36.250 --> 17:38.030
Did you catch a glimpse of the amount?

17:38.030 --> 17:39.560
At least tens of thousands.

17:40.590 --> 17:41.350
Keep a close eye on them.

17:41.350 --> 17:43.940
We'll take them all down
once they get the final payment.

17:43.940 --> 17:46.050
Now that the stash place is confirmed,

17:46.050 --> 17:47.590
stop tailing them in the next few days.

17:47.590 --> 17:48.640
Yes, boss.

17:59.530 --> 17:59.990
Here...

18:00.010 --> 18:01.270
What are you two doing?

18:02.090 --> 18:03.510
Zhuang Zhuang is writing a song.

18:03.510 --> 18:04.840
It's very beautiful.

18:05.030 --> 18:05.790
Not at all.

18:06.070 --> 18:07.090
Mr. Zheng told me to compose

18:07.090 --> 18:08.030
a new song, didn't he?

18:08.030 --> 18:09.050
I just got started and asked

18:09.050 --> 18:11.110
Sophia to play accompaniment for me.

18:12.380 --> 18:13.380
Impressive.

18:13.420 --> 18:14.400
You're still carrying on

18:14.400 --> 18:15.570
with your music stuff on this trip.

18:15.570 --> 18:16.530
I just wrote a rough draft

18:16.530 --> 18:17.730
based on my feelings.

18:17.750 --> 18:19.160
When we're back,
I still need to have it revised

18:19.160 --> 18:19.890
by Mr. Zheng.

18:20.200 --> 18:20.730
Alright.

18:21.530 --> 18:22.790
Let me be the audience.

18:24.380 --> 18:24.850
Okay.

18:25.220 --> 18:26.140
Shall we start over

18:26.140 --> 18:27.350
using the melody

18:27.550 --> 18:28.350
we just played?

18:28.350 --> 18:28.770
Sure.

18:29.920 --> 18:33.030
One, two, three, four.

18:52.960 --> 18:55.490
You should write this down.
It sounds lovely.

19:10.750 --> 19:11.640
It's really nice.

19:11.640 --> 19:12.900
The song sounds great.

19:13.850 --> 19:14.960
Thank you, Sophia.

19:15.310 --> 19:16.330
Such a beautiful song.

19:16.330 --> 19:17.530
The accompaniment was beautiful too.

19:17.530 --> 19:19.130
Xiaojun, did it go smoothly?

19:19.290 --> 19:19.830
Yes.

19:20.740 --> 19:22.090
Where did you guys go today?

19:22.090 --> 19:23.630
We were off to hide money.

19:23.900 --> 19:24.740
Hide money?

19:25.770 --> 19:26.680
Sophia has introduced

19:26.680 --> 19:27.880
so many clients to us.

19:28.090 --> 19:28.680
Recently,

19:28.680 --> 19:29.880
we've received a lot of deposits.

19:29.880 --> 19:32.180
There'll be large final payments
when the goods arrive.

19:32.180 --> 19:34.210
So, we stashed the money

19:34.400 --> 19:35.850
in the lockers in batches.

19:35.850 --> 19:37.180
And those people
really fell for our trick.

19:37.180 --> 19:38.180
Sergey must think

19:38.180 --> 19:39.000
everything's under his control.

19:39.000 --> 19:40.220
But he could never imagine

19:40.220 --> 19:42.750
that we actually swapped the money
in the end.

19:42.830 --> 19:43.960
Shengli is so smart.

19:44.000 --> 19:45.800
This is an absolutely brilliant

19:45.940 --> 19:46.790
idea of his.

19:48.510 --> 19:49.880
When the last batch of goods arrives,

19:49.880 --> 19:51.940
it'll be time to confront Mr. Sergey.

19:53.200 --> 19:55.010
Xiaojun has been clamoring
for mutton hot pot

19:55.010 --> 19:56.400
since yesterday.

19:56.830 --> 19:57.700
What is this?

19:57.700 --> 19:59.360
Are we cooking meat with this?

19:59.500 --> 20:00.570
Aren't you ignorant, goof?

20:00.570 --> 20:01.510
This is a samovar.

20:01.510 --> 20:02.420
For making tea?

20:02.530 --> 20:03.010
Yes.

20:03.420 --> 20:05.180
The copper pot Xiaojun brought me

20:05.180 --> 20:06.640
was taken by my friend.

20:06.770 --> 20:08.050
This looks exquisite.

20:08.160 --> 20:08.900
Yes.

20:09.550 --> 20:11.480
How about I bring you one
when I deliver goods

20:11.480 --> 20:12.250
to Beijing?

20:12.510 --> 20:13.050
Great.

20:13.420 --> 20:15.420
Then I'll also send you a copper pot
when I get back.

20:15.420 --> 20:15.880
Okay.

20:16.230 --> 20:17.400
Although this is a samovar,

20:17.400 --> 20:18.220
it actually has

20:18.220 --> 20:19.750
the same usage as a copper pot.

20:19.750 --> 20:20.940
Take out that bottle of Erguotou then.

20:20.940 --> 20:21.880
Why not have a few drinks tonight?

20:21.880 --> 20:22.420
Sure.

20:22.750 --> 20:25.090
But I must roll up the carpet first.

20:25.960 --> 20:26.530
No, I won't barf.

20:26.530 --> 20:28.030
Erguotou agrees well with me.

20:28.030 --> 20:29.200
Right? I've had it before with Shengli.

20:29.200 --> 20:29.960
I can manage.

20:29.980 --> 20:31.440
Okay, I'll go find it then.

20:32.140 --> 20:33.990
And I'll go help her with it.

20:34.720 --> 20:35.570
Didn't I bring

20:35.570 --> 20:37.220
that bottle of Erguoto to you

20:37.290 --> 20:38.770
along with that pile of tea leaves?

20:38.770 --> 20:40.900
Such a good life they're having here.

20:51.330 --> 20:52.460
Good take. We got it!

20:52.590 --> 20:54.140
Let's congratulate Ms. Shen Ranran

20:54.140 --> 20:55.400
on wrapping up the filming!

20:55.400 --> 20:57.070
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

20:58.330 --> 20:59.130
Thank you all.

20:59.880 --> 21:00.460
Thanks.

21:02.980 --> 21:04.040
Congratulations.

21:04.200 --> 21:04.920
Good work.

21:04.920 --> 21:05.780
Thank you, sir.

21:05.960 --> 21:06.960
Sure. We must work together again

21:06.960 --> 21:07.940
if there's a chance. Alright?

21:07.940 --> 21:08.660
Definitely.

21:08.660 --> 21:10.880
-Everyone, good work!
-Thanks for the hard work, everyone!

21:10.880 --> 21:11.420
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

21:11.420 --> 21:13.080
Your performance was spot on.

21:15.530 --> 21:16.250
Ranran,

21:16.770 --> 21:18.630
I have a piece of good news for you.

21:20.440 --> 21:22.170
The crew just called and told me

21:22.610 --> 21:24.400
how wonderful your acting was,

21:24.850 --> 21:27.610
and that you're a nice
and professional actress.

21:28.530 --> 21:29.990
That gave me so much pride,

21:30.090 --> 21:30.620
for real.

21:31.890 --> 21:32.750
Do you remember?

21:32.750 --> 21:33.880
You told me before

21:34.290 --> 21:34.960
that you hoped

21:34.960 --> 21:36.010
the crew would thank me

21:36.010 --> 21:37.180
for recommending

21:37.200 --> 21:38.510
a good actress to them.

21:39.250 --> 21:40.450
Now, it has come true.

21:44.160 --> 21:47.020
Making a romantic gesture
right after your return?

21:47.250 --> 21:49.850
Waiting for Ranran again,
aren't you, Mr. Tao?

21:50.980 --> 21:51.700
Yes, I am.

21:55.740 --> 21:56.720
Listen,

21:56.750 --> 21:57.510
Ranran said

21:57.570 --> 21:59.250
she would come back today,
but she didn't give

21:59.250 --> 22:00.180
a specific time.

22:00.380 --> 22:02.320
You might have to wait till dusk today.

22:02.320 --> 22:03.720
I'll only do that for her.

22:03.960 --> 22:06.090
I won't wait that long for anyone else.

22:06.500 --> 22:07.400
Now that you've made money,

22:07.400 --> 22:09.130
you sound much more confident.

22:11.050 --> 22:12.250
Let me treat you to...

22:13.000 --> 22:14.180
Mending Meat Pies.

22:14.350 --> 22:15.080
Sounds nice!

22:16.070 --> 22:16.550
What do you think?

22:16.550 --> 22:17.310
Do keep your word.

22:17.310 --> 22:17.700
Sure.

22:19.380 --> 22:20.910
Alright, talk to you later!

22:27.960 --> 22:28.650
Look at you,

22:28.680 --> 22:30.210
you must've done a good job.

22:31.220 --> 22:33.080
-Ranran!
-Our superstar is back.

22:33.750 --> 22:34.770
So beautiful.

22:34.790 --> 22:35.790
You're so pretty.

22:37.700 --> 22:39.010
I keep telling everyone I meet

22:39.010 --> 22:40.050
that a superstar, Ranran, has risen

22:40.050 --> 22:41.590
amongst us in the Seasons Change Hostel.

22:41.590 --> 22:42.850
Don't forget about us.

22:42.900 --> 22:43.770
No, I won't.

22:43.770 --> 22:45.160
You're indeed different now, superstar.

22:45.160 --> 22:46.240
All right, guys.

22:46.480 --> 22:47.850
Many people await our superstar.

22:47.850 --> 22:49.050
Have some tact, guys.

22:49.290 --> 22:50.660
You can talk to Ranran later.

22:50.660 --> 22:51.240
Go do your things.

22:51.240 --> 22:51.720
Bye!

22:51.720 --> 22:52.000
Bye.

22:52.000 --> 22:53.400
I'll talk to you tonight.

22:53.480 --> 22:54.610
Bye, we're leaving!

23:04.270 --> 23:05.660
Wang, who lives by the alley entrance,

23:05.660 --> 23:06.590
gave me this.

23:09.380 --> 23:10.320
If you like it...

23:12.810 --> 23:13.740
then it's yours.

23:17.070 --> 23:17.800
Liangliang!

23:23.280 --> 23:25.480
Oh right, I forgot to congratulate you.

23:25.500 --> 23:27.300
Congrats on finishing filming.

23:28.810 --> 23:30.260
Ranran, you're back?

23:30.480 --> 23:31.090
Ranran.

23:31.220 --> 23:33.090
Ranran, I missed you so much.

23:33.220 --> 23:34.420
You're finally back.

23:34.700 --> 23:35.240
Liangliang,

23:35.240 --> 23:36.460
look how great Ranran turned out.

23:36.460 --> 23:37.680
She has become a superstar now.

23:37.680 --> 23:38.590
You're so lucky.

23:38.590 --> 23:38.980
Exactly.

23:38.980 --> 23:39.480
You must

23:39.480 --> 23:40.590
treat Ranran well.

23:43.140 --> 23:44.750
Look, he's turned shy, hasn't he?

23:44.750 --> 23:45.490
Look at him.

23:45.850 --> 23:46.570
How was your work on the film set?

23:46.570 --> 23:47.070
Was it tiring?

23:47.070 --> 23:50.330
-I'm curious about your life there.
-Yes. Tell us about it.

24:17.510 --> 24:18.570
Where is the money?

24:20.420 --> 24:22.000
Money? What money?

24:25.740 --> 24:26.250
We got you

24:26.250 --> 24:27.380
so many goods.

24:28.500 --> 24:29.430
Won't you pay up?

24:30.420 --> 24:31.820
I did underestimate you.

24:31.850 --> 24:33.290
I never expected you guys could get

24:33.290 --> 24:35.200
so many goods within just a few days.

24:35.200 --> 24:36.530
I've figured it out now.

24:37.180 --> 24:39.070
You have no intention
of paying even a penny,

24:39.070 --> 24:39.610
do you?

24:40.810 --> 24:42.000
Yes, I'm not going to pay.

24:42.000 --> 24:42.580
So what?

24:42.750 --> 24:44.150
You are not welcome here.

24:49.680 --> 24:51.140
What if I insist on staying here today?

24:51.140 --> 24:51.740
Jun.

24:57.770 --> 24:59.100
Then stay here forever.

24:59.110 --> 25:00.350
Don't! Don't hurt us!

25:00.530 --> 25:02.380
Harmony brings wealth.

25:03.000 --> 25:04.200
You've checked our goods.

25:04.200 --> 25:05.270
They're of high quality.

25:05.270 --> 25:06.870
We will come back here again.

25:06.980 --> 25:08.200
If your sales are strong

25:08.200 --> 25:09.240
and you get market traction,

25:09.240 --> 25:10.790
we can be long-term partners

25:10.790 --> 25:12.390
and make big money together!

25:14.590 --> 25:17.250
This is what a good friend of ours
should be like.

25:17.290 --> 25:19.240
Well, let's celebrate in advance

25:19.260 --> 25:21.120
for our successful cooperation.

25:21.900 --> 25:22.590
Jun.

25:38.400 --> 25:40.870
They even brought
a bottle of alcohol here,

25:41.500 --> 25:43.140
attempting to threaten us.

25:52.880 --> 25:54.610
While Sergey is selling goods,

25:54.830 --> 25:55.940
I've booked the earliest train tickets.

25:55.940 --> 25:57.540
Let's hurry back to Beijing.

25:58.510 --> 26:00.210
Your stay here was so short.

26:00.510 --> 26:02.370
I didn't get to properly host you.

26:03.350 --> 26:04.420
I prepared some

26:04.440 --> 26:06.100
Russian specialties for you.

26:06.440 --> 26:08.270
Let's have a gathering next time.

26:08.270 --> 26:09.730
Thank you. How kind of you.

26:09.980 --> 26:12.120
Sorry for causing you trouble this time.

26:12.120 --> 26:13.220
We will miss you.

26:13.510 --> 26:15.080
I will miss you too.

26:17.030 --> 26:19.140
Sophia, thank you.

26:19.810 --> 26:20.470
No problem.

26:21.960 --> 26:22.960
Do often visit me.

26:25.000 --> 26:26.780
How about I give you a ride?

26:26.810 --> 26:27.500
N-No need.

26:28.590 --> 26:29.330
Your car is too noticeable.

26:29.330 --> 26:30.260
Sergey knows it.

26:30.740 --> 26:31.460
We've called another car.

26:31.460 --> 26:32.510
It's safer that way.

26:32.510 --> 26:33.400
We can't let them notice

26:33.400 --> 26:34.530
that we are leaving.

26:34.810 --> 26:35.830
Right. Zhuang Zhuang,

26:35.830 --> 26:36.770
the two of you will leave first,

26:36.770 --> 26:38.760
while I lure them away
by pretending to deposit money.

26:38.760 --> 26:39.570
We'll meet up at the train station.

26:39.570 --> 26:40.400
No.

26:40.700 --> 26:41.740
I must stick with you.

26:41.740 --> 26:43.010
Listen to me.

26:43.090 --> 26:43.920
I can run faster

26:43.920 --> 26:45.310
if I'm all by myself.

26:45.460 --> 26:47.010
That's right, Zhuang Zhuang.

26:47.010 --> 26:48.350
Shengli and I have worked it all out.

26:48.350 --> 26:49.080
Don't worry.

26:49.740 --> 26:51.340
Shengli, play things by ear.

26:51.510 --> 26:52.970
Leave Zhuang Zhuang to me.

26:53.030 --> 26:55.290
I'll surely get her to the train station.

26:58.580 --> 27:00.040
Can you manage on your own?

27:00.270 --> 27:01.470
Yes, don't you worry.

27:01.750 --> 27:02.310
Sophia.

27:14.940 --> 27:15.970
You see,

27:17.290 --> 27:17.940
no one knows

27:17.940 --> 27:20.270
when we'll meet again after this parting.

27:20.830 --> 27:23.090
I've always wanted to ask you a question.

27:29.420 --> 27:30.700
How come a pretty lady

27:31.610 --> 27:33.870
such as yourself hasn't got married yet?

27:36.980 --> 27:39.250
What are your requirements

27:41.380 --> 27:43.110
for your future spouse?

27:44.700 --> 27:45.560
I guess I just

27:45.590 --> 27:47.250
haven't met the right person.

27:48.500 --> 27:50.070
Actually, I'm not asking much.

27:50.070 --> 27:51.670
A bouquet of flowers will do.

27:54.310 --> 27:54.920
Got it.

27:55.590 --> 27:56.650
That's nice. Okay.

28:07.140 --> 28:08.240
What was wrong with you? Did you go blind?

28:08.240 --> 28:09.750
I told you to keep close watch on them.

28:09.750 --> 28:11.590
I saw them place the money there
with my own eyes.

28:11.590 --> 28:13.340
I don't know
how things turned out like this!

28:13.340 --> 28:14.570
What gibberish are you giving me?

28:14.570 --> 28:16.090
Go find those people now!

28:16.110 --> 28:18.110
Are we really going to look for them?

28:31.930 --> 28:33.440
[Bacui Trading Co., Ltd.]

28:40.510 --> 28:41.070
Didn't we agree

28:41.070 --> 28:42.930
to go straight to the restaurant?

28:42.940 --> 28:44.670
Why do we have to assemble here?

28:48.980 --> 28:49.720
Where is the money?

28:49.720 --> 28:50.650
Ask him instead.

28:51.270 --> 28:52.050
No, ask him.

28:53.310 --> 28:54.440
I gave him the money,

28:54.550 --> 28:55.270
but he lost it.

28:55.270 --> 28:56.540
How was it my fault?

28:56.980 --> 28:58.110
Could I have gotten it back?

28:58.110 --> 28:59.350
I was robbed halfway and merely

28:59.350 --> 29:00.000
made it back!

29:00.000 --> 29:00.630
Just drop it.

29:00.630 --> 29:01.660
You're six feet tall.

29:01.660 --> 29:02.680
You could've fought him!

29:02.680 --> 29:03.330
Me fighting him?

29:03.330 --> 29:04.350
Alright, enough.

29:04.400 --> 29:05.610
Stop bickering.

29:06.270 --> 29:07.400
I was far away when you had me

29:07.400 --> 29:08.180
pick up a delivery.

29:08.180 --> 29:09.290
Am I a post office now?

29:09.290 --> 29:11.110
Can this thing be more important
than money?

29:11.110 --> 29:12.090
What's inside?

29:12.220 --> 29:13.820
Open it and see for yourself.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.440
You didn't bring the money back,

29:28.510 --> 29:30.380
so you got a trophy cup instead, huh?

29:30.380 --> 29:31.580
It's not a trophy cup,

29:32.920 --> 29:34.270
but a Russian samovar.

29:35.050 --> 29:37.400
In Russian, it's called "самова́р."

29:38.110 --> 29:40.100
Sophia gave it to us

29:40.330 --> 29:41.610
as a souvenir.

29:41.700 --> 29:42.240
It is filled

29:42.240 --> 29:43.370
with her love for us.

29:43.500 --> 29:45.200
How much love can fit into this?

29:45.200 --> 29:46.800
Only money represents love.

30:01.940 --> 30:04.360
This is truly full of love.

30:05.550 --> 30:06.100
It...

30:06.350 --> 30:07.810
How do Russians call this?

30:10.160 --> 30:11.600
It's called a "samovar."

30:11.740 --> 30:12.660
I bet Sergey must

30:12.660 --> 30:13.860
be furious right now.

30:15.000 --> 30:16.030
Let's go out for dinner.

30:16.030 --> 30:16.740
Let's go.

30:17.000 --> 30:18.130
A celebration, huh?

30:18.140 --> 30:19.800
Come on. Let's go have hot pot.

30:19.850 --> 30:21.060
Hot pot sounds good.

30:21.140 --> 30:21.640
Mutton hot pot.

30:21.640 --> 30:22.170
Let's go!

30:22.700 --> 30:25.370
Let's cook the meat with this samovar.

30:34.640 --> 30:36.970
Didn't expect the clothes to freeze, huh?

30:38.420 --> 30:39.200
Wet clothes

30:39.240 --> 30:40.810
shouldn't be hung outside directly.

30:40.810 --> 30:41.980
See, all frozen up, aren't they?

30:41.980 --> 30:42.810
Don't touch it.

30:42.810 --> 30:44.740
Careful. They could easily break.

30:45.160 --> 30:47.180
Take them indoors
and put them on the heater.

30:47.180 --> 30:48.980
It'll also add to the moisture
in the room.

30:48.980 --> 30:50.400
I can't take these back to Room 108.

30:50.400 --> 30:51.240
Our heater is fully

30:51.240 --> 30:52.640
covered by smelly socks.

30:52.880 --> 30:53.670
Impressive.

30:53.900 --> 30:56.560
You're an expert on everything
home and travel.

30:56.790 --> 30:59.080
Not everything.

30:59.270 --> 31:00.250
There's one thing

31:00.250 --> 31:01.420
that I really need

31:01.460 --> 31:03.390
your advice on, Ms. Zhuang Zhuang.

31:03.770 --> 31:04.440
What is it?

31:13.060 --> 31:14.980
[Spring Grass]

31:14.090 --> 31:15.060
Lyrics?

31:15.270 --> 31:16.600
Didn't you say new songs

31:16.610 --> 31:18.740
could get extra points in the contest?

31:23.920 --> 31:25.240
When did you write this?

31:25.240 --> 31:26.160
Back when we were in Russia.

31:26.160 --> 31:27.760
I made a draft at that time.

31:28.000 --> 31:29.920
After our return, I pulled some strings

31:29.920 --> 31:30.920
and asked a musician friend

31:30.920 --> 31:31.980
for some pointers.

31:32.140 --> 31:33.960
When you sang
with Sophia playing the accordion

31:33.960 --> 31:34.980
as an accompaniment,

31:34.980 --> 31:36.740
I roughly jotted down the melody.

31:36.740 --> 31:37.500
Try putting them together.

31:37.500 --> 31:38.420
I'll fix the lyrics if there is

31:38.420 --> 31:39.350
anything wrong.

31:41.590 --> 31:43.550
How about I sing it to you

31:43.590 --> 31:44.330
now?

31:44.810 --> 31:46.030
You know how to sing it?

31:46.030 --> 31:47.160
I-I can give it a try.

31:47.200 --> 31:49.130
I learned something from the guys.

31:52.810 --> 31:59.420
Grow wild like spring grass.

31:59.640 --> 32:00.940
I embrace the galaxy

32:00.980 --> 32:03.900
in the gentle...

32:02.510 --> 32:04.550
[Spring Grass]

32:03.900 --> 32:07.640
In the gentle evening breeze.

32:08.050 --> 32:12.460
In the gentle evening breeze.

32:12.960 --> 32:17.060
The sky slowly brightens into dawn.

32:17.140 --> 32:19.740
Let me sing a song.

32:20.050 --> 32:22.960
Unyielding even in cracks,

32:23.460 --> 32:25.510
wild grass thrives...

32:25.660 --> 32:31.720
In the lushness of spring.

32:32.070 --> 32:37.350
In the lushness of spring.

32:39.750 --> 32:40.610
It sounds nice.

32:42.310 --> 32:43.220
Sing it again.

32:43.830 --> 32:44.400
Okay.

32:47.350 --> 32:54.350
Grow wild like spring grass.

33:30.200 --> 33:31.930
Let's have something foreign.

33:32.070 --> 33:33.610
A bottle of vodka, please.

33:34.810 --> 33:35.720
What did you say?

33:35.720 --> 33:37.180
A bottle of vodka, please.

33:37.380 --> 33:38.330
Okay, just a minute.

33:38.330 --> 33:39.380
Vodka.

33:39.530 --> 33:40.880
I'm speaking Russian
with a bit of an accent...

33:40.880 --> 33:41.510
Jun.

33:41.720 --> 33:42.250
Jun.

33:42.500 --> 33:42.900
Jun.

33:42.920 --> 33:44.050
Hurry, take a seat.

33:46.310 --> 33:47.530
Why are you so sulky?

33:47.770 --> 33:48.570
What's wrong?

33:49.200 --> 33:50.730
Extreme joy begets sorrow.

33:52.270 --> 33:53.130
What happened?

33:53.770 --> 33:54.700
Since our trip to Russia

33:54.700 --> 33:55.610
till this day,

33:56.290 --> 33:57.140
the exchange rate

33:57.140 --> 33:59.120
has dropped by more than half.

33:59.220 --> 34:01.550
It decreased by 0.8 just yesterday alone.

34:02.850 --> 34:03.790
A decrease of 0.8...

34:03.790 --> 34:05.220
H-How serious is that?

34:05.770 --> 34:07.220
I can't even calculate it.

34:07.220 --> 34:08.820
Anyway, it's a huge loss.

34:12.980 --> 34:13.840
How about this?

34:14.280 --> 34:15.340
Today's dinner...

34:17.070 --> 34:17.820
will cost a lot.

34:17.820 --> 34:19.380
Shall we split the bill?

34:19.730 --> 34:20.480
What do you think?

34:20.480 --> 34:21.080
Fine by me.

34:21.550 --> 34:22.350
-Sure.
-Okay.

34:24.460 --> 34:24.900
Sir,

34:25.010 --> 34:25.800
the vodka you ordered.

34:25.800 --> 34:26.340
We don't want it now.

34:26.340 --> 34:26.960
Get us beers instead.

34:26.960 --> 34:28.010
Three beers, please.

34:28.010 --> 34:28.820
How can we not drink vodka?

34:28.820 --> 34:29.880
We'll take it. Thanks.

34:29.880 --> 34:30.230
Okay.

34:30.230 --> 34:30.710
Enjoy.

34:30.710 --> 34:31.150
Thanks.

34:31.150 --> 34:31.900
I-It is expensive.

34:31.900 --> 34:32.630
For what it's worth,

34:32.630 --> 34:33.960
today calls for a celebration.

34:33.960 --> 34:35.489
We've made money after all.

34:35.500 --> 34:37.510
Yes. Don't just focus on the losses.

34:37.550 --> 34:39.000
We've got profits, right?

34:39.000 --> 34:39.540
Right.

34:39.570 --> 34:41.199
I-I did have

34:41.230 --> 34:43.050
a pretty good time on this trip.

34:45.800 --> 34:46.960
I'll level with you.

34:48.860 --> 34:50.320
We didn't make much money.

34:50.840 --> 34:51.780
I went to the bank

34:52.300 --> 34:53.960
and queued for over two hours.

34:54.820 --> 34:55.760
This is all I got.

34:58.150 --> 34:59.020
Only 300?

34:59.050 --> 35:00.550
M-My investment alone was 900.

35:00.550 --> 35:02.080
Jun, are you joking with us?

35:13.400 --> 35:14.860
I couldn't squeeze a tear.

35:16.960 --> 35:19.090
I promised to help you guys make money.

35:20.670 --> 35:21.500
But I failed—

35:22.730 --> 35:24.790
how was that possible?

35:26.300 --> 35:27.300
Look what this is!

35:27.820 --> 35:28.320
Gosh.

35:28.980 --> 35:30.240
This is what we earned.

35:30.510 --> 35:31.870
This is what we earned.

35:32.210 --> 35:33.740
This is also what we earned.

35:33.800 --> 35:34.950
What is this?

35:35.150 --> 35:36.060
What is this?

35:36.130 --> 35:37.170
This much?

35:37.360 --> 35:38.360
Of course!

35:38.860 --> 35:40.110
Even brothers must
settle accounts clearly.

35:40.110 --> 35:41.500
Let's divide the money now.

35:41.500 --> 35:43.740
Well, your investment was 3000 yuan.

35:44.280 --> 35:45.380
So naturally,

35:45.420 --> 35:46.480
you should receive

35:46.500 --> 35:48.300
a total profit of 25,000, right?

35:48.570 --> 35:50.070
As for me, I paid for half of the cost.

35:50.070 --> 35:51.200
This should be mine.

35:51.510 --> 35:54.160
And this... is what you earned.

35:54.340 --> 35:56.780
But I think you deserve more.

35:57.280 --> 35:58.110
I'll give you 3,000 extra.

35:58.110 --> 35:58.920
So you'll have 8,000 in total.

35:58.920 --> 35:59.920
What do you think?

36:00.010 --> 36:01.340
See, what did I tell you?

36:01.400 --> 36:03.930
Good luck finds you
when you're with Lucky Ma!

36:03.960 --> 36:05.440
I not only brought you back
safe and sound,

36:05.440 --> 36:06.710
but also helped you rake in profits.

36:06.710 --> 36:09.240
Good luck finds you
when you're with Lucky Ma!

36:09.420 --> 36:10.650
Come on, what are you waiting for?

36:10.650 --> 36:11.710
Dazed, aren't you?

36:11.840 --> 36:13.920
Well, I only invested 900.

36:14.420 --> 36:16.090
But I was given this much in return.

36:16.090 --> 36:18.000
I-I shouldn't take the extra.

36:18.070 --> 36:19.400
They should split this.

36:19.460 --> 36:20.150
Okay.

36:20.360 --> 36:20.820
Don't!

36:21.090 --> 36:23.150
If next time I invest more,

36:23.150 --> 36:24.320
I'll gain more, right?

36:24.320 --> 36:24.840
Of course.

36:24.840 --> 36:26.480
The more you invest, the more you gain.

36:26.480 --> 36:27.610
Buy a car later.

36:27.690 --> 36:29.210
You invested little and earned little,

36:29.210 --> 36:30.820
I still gave you a higher total.

36:30.820 --> 36:31.280
Come on.

36:31.280 --> 36:32.210
Time for drinks, guys.

36:32.210 --> 36:33.190
-Drink up.
-To Mr. Lucky!

36:33.190 --> 36:33.920
To Mr. Lucky!

36:33.940 --> 36:35.170
-Come on.
-Guys, chug it!

36:35.170 --> 36:35.670
Bottoms up!

36:35.670 --> 36:36.110
Bottoms up!

36:36.110 --> 36:36.840
Thanks, Jun!

36:38.930 --> 36:42.730
[No photos] [No smoking]

36:40.110 --> 36:40.840
Mr. Yang.

36:42.000 --> 36:43.200
Let's get in the room.

36:48.960 --> 36:50.510
Are you the singer to record a song here?

36:50.510 --> 36:50.960
Yes.

36:51.150 --> 36:52.230
She is Zhuang Zhuang, the singer

36:52.230 --> 36:53.160
I told you about.

36:53.650 --> 36:54.510
Zhuang Zhuang,

36:55.090 --> 36:55.800
I put some marks

36:55.800 --> 36:56.570
and highlighted

36:56.570 --> 36:57.340
a few key points here.

36:57.340 --> 36:58.000
Take a look.

36:58.030 --> 37:00.420
[No photos] [No smoking]

36:58.300 --> 36:58.760
Sure.

36:59.190 --> 37:00.320
Thank you, Mr. Yang.

37:00.710 --> 37:01.640
Here's the plan.

37:01.800 --> 37:02.440
I'll go in

37:02.440 --> 37:04.070
and adjust the equipment in a bit.

37:04.070 --> 37:04.690
Then, I will

37:04.690 --> 37:06.360
get you in there to familiarize you
with the place.

37:06.360 --> 37:07.730
Stay here and get ready for now,

37:07.730 --> 37:08.060
okay?

37:08.070 --> 37:08.880
Okay.

37:09.300 --> 37:09.670
Sure.

37:24.380 --> 37:30.590
Grow wild like spring grass.

37:30.800 --> 37:38.480
I embrace the galaxy
in the gentle evening breeze.

37:39.010 --> 37:43.050
The sky slowly brightens into dawn.

37:43.170 --> 37:45.660
Let me sing a song.

37:46.090 --> 37:49.100
Unyielding even in cracks,

37:49.380 --> 37:58.230
wild grass thrives
in the lushness of spring.

38:06.010 --> 38:12.230
Grow wild like spring grass.

38:12.590 --> 38:15.010
I embrace the galaxy in...

38:16.440 --> 38:17.610
I'm asking you to sing.

38:17.610 --> 38:19.270
Pretend this is a microphone.

38:22.780 --> 38:25.030
It's fair to say a big task
has been completed.

38:25.030 --> 38:27.560
The effort in the past six months
has paid off.

38:28.010 --> 38:29.120
Above all,

38:29.480 --> 38:32.280
I need to thank you,
Mr. Xu the great screenwriter.

38:33.570 --> 38:35.510
In fact, when I first came to Beijing,

38:35.510 --> 38:38.130
I was totally focused on
becoming a screenwriter.

38:38.130 --> 38:39.840
I even made a resolution

38:40.610 --> 38:41.630
that until I became

38:41.630 --> 38:43.210
a real screenwriter,

38:43.340 --> 38:44.190
I would never consider

38:44.190 --> 38:45.850
any romantic relationships.

38:46.150 --> 38:48.410
Have you ever read martial arts novels?

38:48.920 --> 38:50.500
All the great heroes written in those

38:50.500 --> 38:52.130
have to detach themselves
from worldly desires

38:52.130 --> 38:54.280
when they practice peerless martial arts.

38:54.280 --> 38:55.730
That's roughly it.

38:56.210 --> 38:57.340
But I found...

38:58.730 --> 39:00.730
t-that the two of us...

39:04.530 --> 39:05.390
Zhuang Zhuang!

39:08.340 --> 39:09.200
Zhuang Zhuang!

39:11.070 --> 39:11.930
Zhuang Zhuang!

39:14.150 --> 39:15.010
Zhuang Zhuang!

39:17.150 --> 39:17.570
Zhuang Zhuang!

39:17.570 --> 39:18.230
Xu Shengli!

39:21.760 --> 39:23.690
Zhuang Zhuang, why did you hop off?

39:23.860 --> 39:26.120
You didn't even notice I was left behind.

39:40.570 --> 39:42.070
Are you backing out now?

39:45.960 --> 39:47.980
D-Did you hear what I said?

39:49.280 --> 39:50.210
What did you say?

39:53.730 --> 39:54.860
You know what I said.

39:56.000 --> 39:56.960
What was it?

40:02.710 --> 40:04.110
Please be my girlfriend.

40:16.840 --> 40:18.970
Do you have to think about it that long?

40:49.050 --> 40:49.910
Get on the bike.

40:50.820 --> 40:51.340
Okay.

40:56.960 --> 40:58.810
It's so much warmer this way.

40:59.090 --> 41:00.950
Winter in Beijing is really long.

41:02.210 --> 41:04.070
Spring is approaching, isn't it?

41:05.730 --> 41:08.230
Actually, winter is also quite nice.

41:23.400 --> 41:24.420
I have already

41:24.900 --> 41:26.980
transferred my energy to you.

41:27.900 --> 41:30.420
Next, I'll ask you questions

41:30.730 --> 41:32.590
and you'll give me answers, okay?

41:33.090 --> 41:33.670
Okay.

41:36.210 --> 41:38.230
How many years have you been paralyzed?

41:38.230 --> 41:39.520
More than 20 years.

41:39.860 --> 41:41.500
Do you know why

41:42.190 --> 41:43.230
you could never stand up

41:43.230 --> 41:44.560
during all these years?

41:45.010 --> 41:45.920
No, I don't.

41:47.460 --> 41:49.260
It's because you didn't meet me.

41:50.980 --> 41:52.480
If you had met me earlier,

41:53.320 --> 41:55.720
you would've been able
to stand up long ago.

41:57.300 --> 41:58.660
Suppose I help you

41:58.760 --> 42:01.510
stand up today,

42:02.960 --> 42:04.460
how will you repay me?

42:06.860 --> 42:08.460
However much money you want,

42:08.820 --> 42:10.090
I-I'll pay you!

42:13.030 --> 42:14.930
Money talk is too tacky.

42:15.380 --> 42:17.130
When I meet the right patient,

42:18.400 --> 42:20.800
I won't even charge a dime.

42:21.820 --> 42:24.920
If not, no amount of money
can buy my service.

42:27.190 --> 42:27.800
How kind.

42:28.840 --> 42:30.400
How very kind of you.

42:31.170 --> 42:32.930
Is this how you talk to

42:32.960 --> 42:34.560
a great kind soul, so rudely?

42:34.670 --> 42:35.550
Stand up now.

42:38.010 --> 42:38.870
Don't help him.

42:42.050 --> 42:42.710
Honey...

42:45.000 --> 42:46.010
You've stood up, right?

42:46.010 --> 42:47.870
Master, I can stand on my feet now.

42:49.050 --> 42:50.210
Uncle, actually...

42:51.500 --> 42:52.430
Speak your mind.

42:53.920 --> 42:55.230
I wonder if you could

42:55.610 --> 42:56.120
let me

42:56.230 --> 42:57.420
join your business.
